MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-1249. State ex rel. Gibbs v. Trimble.

Franklin County, No. 93AP-286. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective April 29, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
